pcdp-lint (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Command-line tool for validating PCDP specification files
  * Validates against 13 structural rules
  * Supports strict mode and template listing
  * Provides detailed diagnostic output with line numbers
  * Static binary with no runtime dependencies

